snippet.title: Pokémon Masters EX | New Challenges Await
snippet.description: Pokémon Masters has evolved! Discover a whole new adventure in Pokémon Masters EX. Assemble Trainers and Pokémon to take on exciting 3-on-3 battles! Create a team all your own, and aim for victory in Story Mode, or in the all-new Champion Stadium! The adventure is up to you. New challenges await.
